2008-11-03  Corentin Le Gall <clegall@proformatique.com>

	pf_manager_dtmf
	$Revision$
	$Date$
	DTMF manager events (backport from Asterisk 1.6 for 1.4)

	XIVO needs these Asterisk 1.6 events, in order to filter out
        some ill-timed Unlink/Link events.

